      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAY KEEPING (1) was below best last time when fifth but three back was a Grade 5 winner in quick time at this track. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Can make amends this time. HEY ARNOLD (4) is progressing well scoring last time out (30.12) at this track and bringing up his 2nd career win. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of three starts. Has good early speed so he should be prominent despite the squeeze draw. Leading chance again. LOCO KADE (7) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Kiwi Golfer (30.09) in a Mix. Has the pace to be prominent. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Will give a great sight again. PEAKY GRACE (2) is worth including.",
